<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="light" lang="es"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Derechos - Defensa Licencias AMBA</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#0f1829",
                        "accent-yellow": "#facc15",
                        "background-light": "#ffffff",
                        "background-dark": "#1b212d",
                        "border-gray": "#e2e8f0",
                        "accent": "#facc15",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Manrope", "sans-serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {
                        "DEFAULT": "0.25rem",
                        "lg": "0.5rem",
                        "xl": "0.75rem",
                        "full": "9999px"
                    },
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
        }
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
        }
        .yellow-underline {
            background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, #facc15 0%, #facc15 100%);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: 100% 0.3em;
            background-position: 0 88%;
            transition: background-size 0.25s ease-in;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark text-primary dark:text-white transition-colors duration-200">
<!-- Header Navigation -->
<%- include("partials/header") %>


<main class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 lg:py-20">
<!-- Hero Introduction -->
<section class="text-center mb-12">
<span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 bg-accent-yellow/20 text-primary dark:text-accent-yellow text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full mb-4">
                Información Legal Actualizada 2024
            </span>
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] mb-6">
                Conocé tus derechos ante la <br/>
<span class="yellow-underline">retención de licencias</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Brindamos claridad y respaldo legal para proteger tu derecho a la libre circulación y al trabajo en toda el Área Metropolitana.
            </p>
<div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
<a href="<%= whatsappLink %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
   class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-accent text-primary font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-all">
  Iniciar Defensa Legal
</a>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Asesoramiento inmediato 24/7</p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Rights Highlights Grid -->
<section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-20">
<div class="p-8 border border-border-gray dark:border-white/10 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 shadow-sm">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-accent-yellow text-[10px] font-black uppercase rounded">Derecho Fundamental</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow">balance</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Debido Proceso</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Ninguna autoridad puede retener su licencia de forma permanente sin una resolución judicial firme. Usted tiene derecho a ser oído y presentar su descargo antes de cualquier sanción inhabilitante.
                </p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 border border-border-gray dark:border-white/10 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 shadow-sm">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-accent-yellow text-[10px] font-black uppercase rounded">Restricción Ilegal</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow">fmd_bad</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Límites de Retención</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    La boleta de citación del inculpado (Formulario Naranjado) habilita a conducir por solo 30 días. Superado ese plazo, la retención sin resolución es considerada una privación ilegítima de un derecho.
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Comparison Paths -->
<section class="mb-20">
<div class="text-center mb-12">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Vías de Acción Legal</h2>
<div class="h-1 w-20 bg-accent-yellow mx-auto"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-border-gray dark:border-white/10 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
<div class="p-10 bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-border-gray dark:border-white/10">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
<div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-primary/10 dark:bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">description</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Vía Administrativa</h4>
</div>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mt-1">check_circle</span>
<span class="text-sm">Presentación de descargo ante juzgado de faltas local.</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mt-1">check_circle</span>
<span class="text-sm">Solicitud de prórroga de boleta de citación.</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 mt-1">check_circle</span>
<span class="text-sm">Pago voluntario o reconocimiento de infracción con quita.</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="p-10 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-primary/20">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
<div class="size-10 rounded-full bg-accent-yellow/20 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary dark:text-accent-yellow">account_balance</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Vía Judicial</h4>
</div>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow mt-1">ads_click</span>
<span class="text-sm">Acción de Amparo por derecho al trabajo.</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow mt-1">ads_click</span>
<span class="text-sm">Medida cautelar para restitución inmediata de licencia.</span>
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow mt-1">ads_click</span>
<span class="text-sm">Apelación de sentencias administrativas arbitrarias.</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Professional Driver Section -->
<section class="relative p-1 bg-accent-yellow rounded-3xl mb-20">
<div class="bg-primary text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[1.4rem] overflow-hidden relative">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl">local_shipping</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-accent-yellow text-primary text-xs font-black uppercase rounded">Urgencia Máxima</span>
<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Conductores Profesionales</h2>
</div>
<p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                        Si su licencia es su herramienta de trabajo (Categorías C, D, E), la retención afecta su derecho constitucional a trabajar. Iniciamos procesos de restitución urgente en menos de 48hs hábiles.
                    </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow">verified</span>
                            Prioridad de gestión
                        </div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-yellow">history</span>
                            Plazos acelerados
                        </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="text-center py-12 border-t border-border-gray dark:border-white/10">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-8">¿Necesitás asesoramiento inmediato?</h2>
<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
<a href="<%= whatsappLink %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
   class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-accent text-primary font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-all">
  Iniciar Defensa Ahora
</a>

<div class="flex items-center gap-8 opacity-60">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">lock</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Privacidad Garantizada</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified_user</span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Matrícula Profesional</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
<!-- Footer -->
<%- include("partials/footer") %>
<!-- Floating WhatsApp Button -->
<%- include("partials/floating-whatsapp") %>

</body></html>